org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.output

Class NiReportHtmlRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.output.NiReportHtmlRenderer

  • public class NiReportHtmlRenderer
extends java.lang.Object
    renders the result of running a NiReport to a html string. See NiReportOutputBuilder. You can run this code for debugging reasons by opening http://localhost:9090/rest/data/nireport/ZZZ, where ZZZ = amp_report_id in the database
